I buy a lot of fan art at conventions.  A small art portfolio bag can be handy to carry any prints you buy without worrying about them getting folded. as packing idea for a convention day as a cosplayer, would highly suggest a tiny sewing kit if you're comfortable with a needle and thread. Accidents can happen on the floor, and if you can fix a tiny rip before it grows, it would make your day last longer.
